After a thorough scan of all provided resolutions, it's clear that none of them directly address the restructuring of "Phường Đông Sơn, Thị xã Bỉm Sơn, Tỉnh Thanh Hóa." The "Other resolutions" section doesn't provide the answer for this specific case. I will have to look into other resources.
